Dependencies
============

Debian
------

aptitude install ocaml-native-compilers ocaml-findlib libfindlib-ocaml-dev libevent-dev libcurl4-gnutls-dev
git clone git://repo.or.cz/ocaml-event.git
git clone git://repo.or.cz/ocurl.git
git clone http://git.ocamlcore.org/extunix/extunix.git
(cd ocaml-event && make all allopt uninstall install)
(cd ocurl && git checkout -b temp && git merge origin/event -m "merge event branch" && ./configure && make all uninstall install && git checkout master)
(cd extunix && ./configure && make build uninstall install)
aptitude install libextlib-ocaml-dev libpcre-ocaml-dev libocamlnet-ocaml-dev libzip-ocaml-dev libocsigen-xhtml-ocaml-dev libounit-ocaml-dev
